{"tid":1807601,"cid":5,"subCid":12,"title":"恒生銀行1965年後成為匯豐集團成員...","createTime":"2020-01-02T02:07:11.000Z","updateTime":"2020-01-02T03:29:13.000Z","uid":344053,"like":6,"dislike":15,"uniUserReply":16,"replies":[{"pid":"00cc81f5fbd52874a96c3ffce9cc2fa751668608","tid":1807601,"uid":344053,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-01-02T02:07:11.000Z","msg":"目前以香港及中國大陸業務為重點。<br />\n<br />\n=] 我明白好多人對佢情有獨鐘，但真係唔好意思，如果匯豐需要呵護，恆生唔該愛埋一份。<br />\n<br />\n~~~~屌你老母尋晚工會旗陣都掟TG，屌...........咩都想裝修。"},{"pid":"b5a1aca1190628906537ac8410c634b800ba983e","tid":1807601,"uid":56633,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-02T02:24:12.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"64ee3ece0432d0d4d4947e2160418c3492b0c9e9","tid":1807601,"uid":948,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-02T02:28:27.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />堅決反對"},{"pid":"5a7cdb07ebb931ae12d5bd2a87123944c1ad313d","tid":1807601,"uid":126305,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-01-02T02:29:13.000Z","msg":"全家用恆生"},{"pid":"c332360163cbf07b9c83709ab7d424eab9e8cc3b","tid":1807601,"uid":79563,"like":1,"dislike":3,"score":-2,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2020-01-02T02:29:48.000Z","msg":"恒生係比匯豐銀行敵意收購<br />\n<br />\n恒生到今日都想自己獨立返"},{"pid":"4e725afa9c22270aa40417f947b3b01172b9222a","tid":1807601,"uid":470,"like":5,"dislike":1,"score":4,"quote":{"pid":"c332360163cbf07b9c83709ab7d424eab9e8cc3b","tid":1807601,"uid":79563,"like":1,"dislike":3,"score":-2,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2020-01-02T02:29:48.000Z","msg":"恒生係比匯豐銀行敵意收購<br />\n<br />\n恒生到今日都想自己獨立返"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-01-02T02:30:29.000Z","msg":"恒生係人？"},{"pid":"dd4efb37082c42896cff282ff0b8ca47fb5cd675","tid":1807601,"uid":33028,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"c332360163cbf07b9c83709ab7d424eab9e8cc3b","tid":1807601,"uid":79563,"like":1,"dislike":3,"score":-2,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2020-01-02T02:29:48.000Z","msg":"恒生係比匯豐銀行敵意收購<br />\n<br />\n恒生到今日都想自己獨立返"